'''海爾舍姆'''（Hailsham）是[[英國|英國]][[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[東薩塞克斯郡|東薩塞克斯郡]]的一個城鎮和[[民政教區|民政教區]]，也是威爾登區的五個城鎮中最大的一座<ref name=EX123>OS Explorer map Eastbourne and Beachy Head Scale: 1:25 000. Publisher:Ordnance Survey – Southampton B2 edition. Publishing Date:2009. ISBN 978 0319240823</ref>。據2011年英國人口普查，海爾舍姆有人口20,476人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=11124121&c=Hailsham&d=16&e=62&g=6421871&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&m=0&r=1&s=1444402026288&enc=1|title=Town population 2011|accessdate=9 October 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304095351/http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=11124121&c=Hailsham&d=16&e=62&g=6421871&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&m=0&r=1&s=1444402026288&enc=1|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

